Charity.create(name: 'Mission Fresh Air', city: 'San Francisco', state: 'CA', discription: 'It is our mission to show people across the United States what fresh air should really taste like. To accomplish this, we are delivering fresh Alaskan air in mason jars to people"s doorsteps. The goal of selling Alaskan air is to raise money for local clean air initiatives.', causes: 'Environment', image: 'https://media.licdn.com/media-proxy/ext?w=542&h=358&f=&hash=3a5sO75p%2BYPOs58JZdqC2R8wJX8%3D&ora=1%2CaFBCTXdkRmpGL2lvQUFBPQ%2CxAVta9Er0Vinkhwfjw8177yE41y87UNCVordEGXyD3u0qYrdf3foecGNKOHyuV1FfigclAMzf_KhFTHiD5LoLo7sftQj3sG3I424ZxUBbFImi24')
Charity.create(name: 'Give A Meal', city: 'San Francisco', state: 'CA', discription: 'We constantly hear about world hunger on the news and there are hundreds of organizations out there trying to solve this issue. But what can we do about local hunger? Hundreds of people in our own neighborhoods are hungry. These are people that have lived beside us for years, paid taxes, raised kids, and are now down on their luck. Here at Give A Meal we want to help these people in our backyards by giving them a free meal, from a local restaurant, for every $10 donated. Together, the goal is to give our neighbors some help and maybe change their luck a bit.', causes: 'Hunger', image: 'https://media.licdn.com/media-proxy/ext?w=543&h=384&f=&hash=%2B9NciSEvxotXQVojPwncvMRA1to%3D&ora=1%2CaFBCTXdkRmpGL2lvQUFBPQ%2CxAVta9Er0Vinkhwfjw8177yE41y87UNCVordEGXyD3u0qYrdf3DqLMTdfeeiuVtCKSsclFI1d_L6R2LnD5Lof9-7eNt5g5ewd424ZxUBbFImi24')


